what you said was

291
00:12:53,100 --> 00:12:55,020
you would leave here if you lost.

292
00:12:55,020 --> 00:12:56,900
You didn't say you would

293
00:12:56,900 --> 00:12:58,060
return the shop to them.

294
00:12:59,500 --> 00:13:00,460
I didn't?

295
00:13:01,620 --> 00:13:02,860
I support you to pay your bet.

296
00:13:02,860 --> 00:13:03,860
But I won't agree

297
00:13:03,860 --> 00:13:04,780
to pay anything else.

298
00:13:07,340 --> 00:13:08,300
So, I had something

299
00:13:08,300 --> 00:13:09,260
in reserve.

300
00:13:09,420 --> 00:13:10,460
That's right.

301
00:13:10,460 --> 00:13:11,900
So, we just need to move out.

302
00:13:12,780 --> 00:13:13,740
But will people think

303
00:13:13,740 --> 00:13:14,780
we're playing a trick?

304
00:13:17,220 --> 00:13:18,180
In this case,

305
00:13:18,180 --> 00:13:19,780
we need some tricks.

306
00:13:35,060 --> 00:13:36,020
All right.

307
00:13:36,260 --> 00:13:37,220
You get some rest.

308
00:13:37,780 --> 00:13:38,620
I'm not tired.

309
00:13:38,620 --> 00:13:39,780
Let me give you a massage.

310
00:13:40,700 --> 00:13:42,020
No need.

311
00:13:42,140 --> 00:13:43,100
I can do it.

312
00:13:43,300 --> 00:13:44,780
You've had a hard time these years.

313
00:13:45,740 --> 00:13:46,660
Let me do it.

314
00:13:47,540 --> 00:13:48,500
I... I...

315
00:13:48,700 --> 00:13:49,620
Sit down.

316
00:13:58,900 --> 00:13:59,860
Nanfeng.

317
00:14:01,820 --> 00:14:03,700
You're no longer what you used to be.

318
00:14:06,860 --> 00:14:07,780
Before,

319
00:14:08,860 --> 00:14:10,780
I was foolish and childish.

320
00:14:11,860 --> 00:14:12,940
When I'm back,

321
00:14:14,420 --> 00:14:15,900
I'll make it up to you and Zhenzhu.

322
00:14:17,820 --> 00:14:19,660
I'll always take care of you.

323
00:14:22,020 --> 00:14:23,900
Don't drink too much wine anymore.

324
00:14:27,980 --> 00:14:29,100
I... I mean...

325
00:14:29,100 --> 00:14:30,540
That's good for your health.

326
00:14:32,740 --> 00:14:33,660
You're right.

327
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:41,540
Getting drunk leads to disasters

328
00:14:43,020 --> 00:14:47,060
and it is too late for regrets.

329
00:14:50,580 --> 00:14:51,500
Dear.

330
00:14:52,140 --> 00:14:53,100
Sit down.

331
00:14:58,210 --> 00:14:59,620
Zhenzhu still ignores you?

332
00:15:00,870 --> 00:15:01,940
It's all my fault.

333
00:15:03,150 --> 00:15:04,220
She isn't to blame.

334
00:15:04,780 --> 00:15:05,700
At that time,

335
00:15:07,820 --> 00:15:08,980
I was too childish

336
00:15:08,980 --> 00:15:10,460
and foolish.

337
00:15:11,580 --> 00:15:13,220
But now, I'm back.

338
00:15:15,740 --> 00:15:18,460
You and I will make this family happy.

339
00:15:32,660 --> 00:15:33,580
Oh,

340
00:15:34,060 --> 00:15:35,020
do you know

341
00:15:35,260 --> 00:15:36,620
where Mother keeps the account books?

342
00:15:39,420 --> 00:15:40,380
Account books?

343
00:15:41,180 --> 00:15:42,140
Why do you ask?

344
00:15:43,380 --> 00:15:44,300
Nothing.

345
00:15:46,740 --> 00:15:48,300
Do you know Luo Aji's secret?

346
00:15:50,220 --> 00:15:51,220
What's his secret?

347
00:15:52,140 --> 00:15:54,940
He's Luo Zhusi's illegitimate son.

348
00:15:55,340 --> 00:15:56,300
What?

349
00:15:57,660 --> 00:15:59,420
Luo... Luo Zhusi...

350
00:15:59,540 --> 00:16:00,460
Illegitimate son?

351
00:16:03,820 --> 00:16:04,780
Are you sure?

352
00:16:05,140 --> 00:16:06,580
My brother knew it a long time ago.

353
00:16:06,780 --> 00:16:08,420
But he was just too kind

354
00:16:08,540 --> 00:16:10,420
to embarrass Zhusi.

355
00:16:10,660 --> 00:16:11,940
This time,

356
00:16:12,260 --> 00:16:13,220
she used Aji Tea

357
00:16:13,220 --> 00:16:14,460
as the name of the tribute tea.

358
00:16:15,500 --> 00:16:16,820
I'm afraid she has schemes

359
00:16:17,380 --> 00:16:18,340
against Jinyu Tea.

360
00:16:21,420 --> 00:16:23,100
Well, what you're saying

361
00:16:23,980 --> 00:16:25,580
sounds reasonable.

362
00:16:25,580 --> 00:16:26,700
I'm just worried

363
00:16:26,700 --> 00:16:27,820
she may have fooled Mother

364
00:16:28,220 --> 00:16:30,340
when I was away.

365
00:16:31,380 --> 00:16:32,380
But don't tell others

366
00:16:32,380 --> 00:16:33,580
about Luo Aji's secret.

367
00:16:34,060 --> 00:16:35,340
I don't want Zhusi

368
00:16:35,500 --> 00:16:38,580
to have a hard time here.

369
00:16:42,420 --> 00:16:43,460
Fine.

370
00:16:51,140 --> 00:16:55,020
(Yuming Chamber)

371
00:16:55,020 --> 00:16:55,940
Grandmother,

372
00:16:56,060 --> 00:16:57,180
under such circumstances,

373
00:16:57,180 --> 00:16:58,100
Sixi and I

374
00:16:58,100 --> 00:16:59,460
will leave here in a day or two.

375
00:17:00,250 --> 00:17:01,570
Hope you'll take care.

376
00:17:02,230 --> 00:17:03,380
Grandmother, take care.

377
00:17:04,180 --> 00:17:06,140
Don't be so stubborn.

378
00:17:07,620 --> 00:17:08,580
Why must you leave?

379
00:17:08,980 --> 00:17:10,620
Last night, your uncle just asked you

380
00:17:10,780 --> 00:17:12,100
not to leave.

381
00:17:12,980 --> 00:17:15,660
This family has just reunited.

382
00:17:15,660 --> 00:17:16,540
Can't you

383
00:17:16,540 --> 00:17:17,820
let me enjoy

384
00:17:18,700 --> 00:17:20,980
a couple of comfortable days?

385
00:17:26,540 --> 00:17:27,580
Jing Kan,

386
00:17:28,620 --> 00:17:29,780
I made a bet with you

387
00:17:30,100 --> 00:17:31,100
because I wanted you

388
00:17:31,110 --> 00:17:32,660
to make better tea.

389
00:17:33,460 --> 00:17:34,980
Now, my purpose has been achieved.

390
00:17:35,620 --> 00:17:36,660
Don't take our bet

391
00:17:37,140 --> 00:17:38,620
so seriously.

392
00:17:39,020 --> 00:17:40,060
I always keep my word.

393
00:17:40,340 --> 00:17:41,260
I proposed the bet,

394
00:17:41,260 --> 00:17:42,180
so I will pay for that.

395
00:17:43,580 --> 00:17:44,500
Grandmother,

396
00:17:45,220 --> 00:17:46,580
we will often come back for you.

397
00:17:48,220 --> 00:17:50,220
Come on, Jing Kan.

398
00:17:50,220 --> 00:17:51,660
Why are you so stubborn?

399
00:17:52,020 --> 00:17:53,500
We're a family.

400
00:17:53,500 --> 00:17:55,620
If you stay, nobody will complain.

401
00:17:55,620 --> 00:17:57,260
- Yeah.
- Let me see who will complain.

402
00:17:57,620 --> 00:17:58,580
Auntie.

403
00:17:59,020 --> 00:17:59,870
Grandmother.

404
00:17:59,870 --> 00:18:00,730
Mother.

405
00:18:01,020 --> 00:18:01,860
Jing Kan just

406
00:18:01,860 --> 00:18:03,100
can't get over it.

407
00:18:04,020 --> 00:18:05,140
Don't bother to persuade him.

408
00:18:06,100 --> 00:18:08,100
My Lady!

409
00:18:09,620 --> 00:18:10,580
What's up?

410
00:18:10,980 --> 00:18:12,580
- My Lady.
- Don't panic.

411
00:18:13,220 --> 00:18:14,180
Lord Pei is here.

412
00:18:14,700 --> 00:18:15,660
Lord Pei?

413
00:18:18,260 --> 00:18:20,100
(Yuming Chamber)
Welcome, Lord Pei.

414
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:22,180
To what do we owe this pleasure?

415
00:18:23,100 --> 00:18:24,020
Ms. Wei,

416
00:18:24,420 --> 00:18:26,340
sorry for this unexpected visit.

417
00:18:26,980 --> 00:18:27,940
Actually,

418
00:18:28,580 --> 00:18:30,060
I'm here for Jing Kan.

419
00:18:34,220 --> 00:18:35,300
Anzhou Sweetie

420
00:18:35,860 --> 00:18:37,260
failed to be the tribute tea.

421
00:18:37,420 --> 00:18:38,860
But what you said yesterday

422
00:18:39,260 --> 00:18:40,820
really impressed me.

423
00:18:41,220 --> 00:18:42,980
A talented young man like you

424
00:18:43,180 --> 00:18:44,900
will have a promising future.

425
00:18:46,660 --> 00:18:47,580
You flatter me, milord.

426
00:18:48,940 --> 00:18:50,260
I want you to do me a favor.

427
00:18:50,900 --> 00:18:51,820
What is it?

428
00:18:52,220 --> 00:18:53,180
Please go on

429
00:18:53,790 --> 00:18:55,380
developing Anzhou Sweetie.

430
00:18:56,940 --> 00:18:57,900
Why?

431
00:19:00,540 --> 00:19:01,700
I want to present it

432
00:19:02,100 --> 00:19:03,180
to His Majesty.

433
00:19:04,140 --> 00:19:05,460
Once His Majesty approves it,

434
00:19:05,860 --> 00:19:07,260
the future of Jinyu Tea

435
00:19:08,020 --> 00:19:09,380
will be very promising.

436
00:19:10,580 --> 00:19:11,660
But there is still room

437
00:19:12,140 --> 00:19:14,180
for the improvement of its flavor.

438
00:19:14,740 --> 00:19:17,060
Hope you'll contribute
to "diversified tea brands"

439
00:19:17,420 --> 00:19:18,340
as you mentioned.

440
00:19:18,740 --> 00:19:19,700
So, tell me.

441
00:19:19,980 --> 00:19:20,940
What do you think?

442
00:19:28,220 --> 00:19:29,180
Milord,

443
00:19:29,620 --> 00:19:31,180
this is our duty.

444
00:19:31,660 --> 00:19:32,540
If we can

445
00:19:32,540 --> 00:19:33,860
make a little contribution

446
00:19:33,980 --> 00:19:35,420
for His Majesty,

447
00:19:35,580 --> 00:19:37,900
we will be really honored.

448
00:19:38,580 --> 00:19:39,500
Jing Kan,

449
00:19:39,780 --> 00:19:40,740
say thank you.

450
00:19:43,380 --> 00:19:44,300
Thank you, milord.

451
00:19:46,420 --> 00:19:47,340
Ms. Wei,

452
00:19:47,660 --> 00:19:49,140
I should go, then.

453
00:19:50,020 --> 00:19:50,980
See you.

454
00:19:50,980 --> 00:19:51,940
Bye.

455
00:19:52,660 --> 00:19:53,580
Let me walk you out.

456
00:20:03,140 --> 00:20:04,100
Will you still leave?

457
00:20:05,740 --> 00:20:07,180
If you still insist,

458
00:20:07,380 --> 00:20:09,340
you'll be really disobedient.

459
00:20:10,220 --> 00:20:11,180
Yeah, Jing Kan.

460
00:20:11,300 --> 00:20:12,940
This family needs you.

461
00:20:12,940 --> 00:20:13,980
Jinyu Tea needs you, too.

462
00:20:14,260 --> 00:20:15,780
Or do you

463
00:20:15,780 --> 00:20:17,580
want me to beg you?

464
00:20:18,460 --> 00:20:19,420
Jing Kan.

465
00:20:21,620 --> 00:20:22,540
Jing Kan.

466
00:20:23,780 --> 00:20:24,660
I know.

467
00:20:24,660 --> 00:20:26,260
If you have to stay like this,

468
00:20:26,260 --> 00:20:27,140
you won't

469
00:20:27,140 --> 00:20:28,140
get over it.

470
00:20:28,540 --> 00:20:29,500
You lost the bet

471
00:20:29,700 --> 00:20:31,180
and you should pay the price.

472
00:20:31,420 --> 00:20:32,380
How about this?

473
00:20:32,740 --> 00:20:33,980
I'll be a peacemaker.

474
00:20:34,220 --> 00:20:35,180
From this day on,

475
00:20:35,180 --> 00:20:36,140
Anzhou Sweetie

476
00:20:36,140 --> 00:20:38,500
won't only be sold in your shop,

477
00:20:38,500 --> 00:20:39,860
but in all the other shops

478
00:20:39,860 --> 00:20:41,940
of Jinyu Tea.

479
00:20:42,060 --> 00:20:43,020
In this way,

480
00:20:43,140 --> 00:20:45,220
people will see

481
00:20:45,220 --> 00:20:47,180
we're united as one

482
00:20:47,420 --> 00:20:48,980
and they'll know you are

483
00:20:48,980 --> 00:20:51,060
a man of his word.

484
00:20:51,180 --> 00:20:52,660
Moreover, we can work together

485
00:20:52,860 --> 00:20:54,140
against the fierce competition

486
00:20:54,140 --> 00:20:56,420
from Laolongtan Tea.

487
00:20:57,260 --> 00:20:58,220
What do you guys think?

488
00:21:01,900 --> 00:21:03,860
Zhusi, what do you say?

489
00:21:05,020 --> 00:21:06,180
You call the shots, Mother.

490
00:21:09,540 --> 00:21:11,900
All right. Let's do this.

491
00:21:24,260 --> 00:21:27,540
(Jail)

492
00:21:53,740 --> 00:21:54,700
Wang,

493
00:21:55,340 --> 00:21:56,260
are you all right?

494
00:22:00,340 --> 00:22:01,260
Where's Zhusi?

495
00:22:02,900 --> 00:22:03,820
Madam hasn't come.

496
00:22:04,180 --> 00:22:05,100
Look at you.

497
00:22:05,460 --> 00:22:06,500
Even if you tried to help,

498
00:22:06,500 --> 00:22:08,060
you shouldn't have kidnapped others.

499
00:22:09,580 --> 00:22:10,500
Oh no.

500
00:22:11,140 --> 00:22:12,740
I must go and explain to her.

501
00:22:12,900 --> 00:22:13,820
No need.

502
00:22:15,340 --> 00:22:16,660
You're fired.

503
00:22:17,900 --> 00:22:18,820
What?

504
00:22:20,260 --> 00:22:21,220
I'm fired?

505
00:22:21,420 --> 00:22:22,340
Yes.

506
00:22:22,620 --> 00:22:23,900
Is it so serious?

507
00:22:23,900 --> 00:22:25,420
Of course.

508
00:22:25,540 --> 00:22:26,900
You did something terrible.

509
00:22:27,140 --> 00:22:28,900
You think you can still be a manager?

510
00:22:29,500 --> 00:22:30,900
Madam sent you to the tea plantation

511
00:22:30,900 --> 00:22:31,900
to assist Liu.

512
00:22:34,180 --> 00:22:35,100
Look at you.

513
00:22:36,340 --> 00:22:37,260
You've lost weight.

514
00:22:38,660 --> 00:22:40,820
Come on. I'll buy you nice food.

515
00:22:44,740 --> 00:22:46,180
You go alone.

516
00:23:01,660 --> 00:23:02,580
Here's the money.

517
00:23:03,540 --> 00:23:04,500
Keep the change.

518
00:23:04,620 --> 00:23:06,020
All right. See you.

519
00:23:26,860 --> 00:23:28,140
How could you do that to me?

520
00:23:31,740 --> 00:23:33,620
I have to be merciless, then.

521
00:23:34,020 --> 00:23:36,300
(Jing Residence)

522
00:23:40,300 --> 00:23:41,260
What's wrong?

523
00:23:42,180 --> 00:23:43,100
I'm upset.

524
00:23:44,620 --> 00:23:45,540
Right.

525
00:23:46,380 --> 00:23:47,580
Since Mr. Jing returned,

526
00:23:48,020 --> 00:23:49,700
he hasn't asked to work for Jinyu Tea.

527
00:23:50,220 --> 00:23:51,580
Neither has Old Lady.

528
00:23:52,580 --> 00:23:53,500
I guess

529
00:23:53,660 --> 00:23:55,660
they must be up to something.

530
00:23:56,860 --> 00:23:57,780
Now,

531
00:23:58,580 --> 00:24:00,420
Aji's work in Jinyu Tea

532
00:24:00,820 --> 00:24:02,460
remains a distant possibility.

533
00:24:03,580 --> 00:24:04,500
Madam,

534
00:24:04,500 --> 00:24:06,180
let's not worry too much.

535
00:24:06,620 --> 00:24:07,740
Only we know

536
00:24:07,740 --> 00:24:08,700
how to make Aji Tea.

537
00:24:09,180 --> 00:24:10,300
I don't think Jing Nanfeng

538
00:24:10,300 --> 00:24:11,620
can stir up too much trouble.

539
00:24:13,180 --> 00:24:15,420
It's not as simple as you say.

540
00:24:19,020 --> 00:24:19,980
What's wrong?

541
00:24:20,900 --> 00:24:21,940
Nothing. I just feel dizzy.

542
00:24:23,620 --> 00:24:24,820
I haven't slept very well.

543
00:24:24,820 --> 00:24:25,860
I have a lot of nightmares.

544
00:24:26,860 --> 00:24:27,780
Nightmares?

545
00:24:28,420 --> 00:24:31,180
Is there anything wrong with the bed?

546
00:24:32,380 --> 00:24:33,340
Mr. Jing has changed

547
00:24:33,340 --> 00:24:34,260
when he's back.

548
00:24:35,180 --> 00:24:37,140
Every night, he washes
his mother's feet.

549
00:24:37,380 --> 00:24:38,740
Now, his family

550
00:24:38,740 --> 00:24:40,180
can count on him.

551
00:24:40,420 --> 00:24:41,500
Think about Mingxia.

552
00:24:41,500 --> 00:24:42,860
Her spine has even stiffened.

553
00:25:34,780 --> 00:25:37,340
I feel something is wrong with Uncle.

554
00:25:38,380 --> 00:25:39,660
He's good, isn't he?

555
00:25:39,980 --> 00:25:41,900
He even helped you to stay.

556
00:25:42,100 --> 00:25:43,260
He gave you a way out.

557
00:25:45,180 --> 00:25:47,540
I just think he pretends

558
00:25:47,540 --> 00:25:48,740
to be kind and caring.

559
00:25:49,140 --> 00:25:49,980
Is he having a scheme

560
00:25:49,980 --> 00:25:51,580
against Jing Kan?

561
00:25:52,620 --> 00:25:53,580
Any proof?

562
00:25:54,020 --> 00:25:54,980
No.

563
00:25:55,740 --> 00:25:57,580
That's why I'm talking to you here.

564
00:25:57,780 --> 00:25:58,740
To me?

565
00:25:59,380 --> 00:26:00,900
You think I can figure it out?

566
00:26:01,380 --> 00:26:02,380
For eating and drinking,

567
00:26:02,380 --> 00:26:03,420
I may give you some advice.

568
00:26:03,780 --> 00:26:04,740
But judging people...

569
00:26:06,740 --> 00:26:08,460
I failed once, you know.

570
00:26:08,860 --> 00:26:09,820
Let's leave it there.

571
00:26:20,100 --> 00:26:21,180
How have you been lately?

572
00:26:22,170 --> 00:26:23,040
Me?

573
00:26:24,420 --> 00:26:25,340
I'm fine.

574
00:26:25,780 --> 00:26:26,980
You can still drink that much?

575
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:29,380
I can always drink that much.

576
00:26:29,940 --> 00:26:30,900
Why do you ask?

577
00:26:31,260 --> 00:26:32,220
Nothing.

578
00:26:32,980 --> 00:26:34,660
I just want to get some evidence

579
00:26:35,340 --> 00:26:36,260
through your drinking.

580
00:26:40,380 --> 00:26:41,820
Come on, No. 357.

581
00:26:42,580 --> 00:26:43,780
The longer I know you,

582
00:26:43,780 --> 00:26:45,860
the more I think people are scheming.

583
00:26:47,060 --> 00:26:49,260
Fine. I'll just get to the point.

584
00:26:49,820 --> 00:26:51,060
I'm thinking

585
00:26:51,220 --> 00:26:52,420
if you can drink with Uncle

586
00:26:52,420 --> 00:26:53,420
and get him drunk.

