632
00:29:38,140 --> 00:29:39,340
She's so drunk.

633
00:29:39,700 --> 00:29:40,660
Let's go.

634
00:29:41,300 --> 00:29:42,340
Get back to sleep.

635
00:29:43,900 --> 00:29:45,100
